            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>V</abbr><ex>ictoriae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>aetus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Moccius <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> Ligus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Marmor, weiß. Raffigurazione della &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Victoria&amp;quot;&amp;quot; su piedistallo; anfora vinaria a destra e animale (capra o stambecco?) a sinistra. (B): Z.1: Mennella, Boccioni: u(t) voverat) s(olvit) l(ibens) l(aetus) m(erito).</p>
            </div>
